'''Third Electoral''' was the session of the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]] during the time of the [[Black Fleet Crisis]]. Although this session was meant to cast a [[Vote of No Confidence/Legends|Vote of No Confidence]] against [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]], instead it became about declaring war against [[Duskhan League]].

